Package uk.gov.gchq.koryphe.impl.function

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Concat
    A Concat is a Function that takes in two objects and calls toString on them and concatenates them together.
    Divide
    A Divide is a Function that takes in two Integers and returns the result of dividing the first by the second.
    DivideBy
    A DivideBy is a Function that takes in an Integer and returns the result of dividing this integer by a pre-configured value.
    Identity
    An Identity is a Function which takes a single object as an input, and simply returns that object.
    Multiply
    A Multiply is a Function that takes in two Integers and returns the result of multiplying the first by the second.
    MultiplyBy
    A MultiplyBy is a Function that takes in an Integer and returns the result of multiplying this integer by a pre-configured value.
    ToString
    A ToString is a Function that takes in an object (null or otherwise), and calls toString on it.
